Keeping the Faith is a 2000 American romantic comedy film written by Stuart Blumberg , and starring Ben Stiller , Edward Norton -LRB- in his directorial debut -RRB- , Jenna Elfman , Eli Wallach , and Anne Bancroft .
This film was released by Touchstone Pictures and Spyglass Entertainment , in association with Triple Threat Talent , on April 14 , 2000 .
The film is dedicated to Norton 's late mother , Robin .
It had a budget of $ 29 million .